{
  "texts": [
    "Everyone could alter video and image files.",
    "This has been possible for some years because of a variety of user-friendly software packages that allow for video, audio, and image editing [10].",
    "Media manipulation has become easier thanks to the widespread use of smartphone apps that perform automated operations like lipsyncing, audio instrumentation, and face swaps [11,12].",
    "In addition, DL-driven advancements have led to many artificial intelligence (AI)-driven technologies that make manipulations highly plausible and credible [13].",
    "Each of these approaches appears to be a beneficial addition to a digital artist's toolkit [14]."
  ]
}